      "type": "html",
      "id": "529157c0fd848af5",
      "text": "<strong>Proposition:</strong> This is because the learning environment created by academic staff development is not a good example of [[Network Learning]]. In particular, it fails to help teachers make connections with other teachers, content, communities and tools."
